---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Boeing Field Limo Service | BFI Airport Car Service | Emerald City Limos"
  description="Premium limo service to Boeing Field / King County International Airport (BFI). Private jet, charter flight and corporate transportation. Meet and greet available. Call (206) 595-9675."
  keywords="boeing field limo service, BFI airport car service, king county international airport transportation, boeing field car service seattle, private jet limo seattle, charter flight transportation seattle"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540339832862-474599807836?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop&q=85"
      alt="Boeing Field King County International Airport limo service"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">BFI Airport</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 drop-shadow-2xl">
        Boeing Field <span class="text-[#d4af37]">Limo Service</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-gray-100">
        Premium private jet and charter flight transportation to King County International Airport
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK BOEING FIELD TRANSFER
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Stats -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-emerald-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">24/7</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Available</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">3 mi</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">From Downtown</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">FBO</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Service Available</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">4.9</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Star Rating</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Boeing Field -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Boeing Field Airport Transportation by <span class="text-emerald-700">Emerald City Limos</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Boeing Field / King County International Airport (BFI) sits just 3 miles south of downtown Seattle, making it the most convenient airport for Seattle city center. It serves private jets, charter flights, cargo operations, and Boeing aircraft test flights.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            For executives, corporate travelers, and private jet passengers, Emerald City Limos provides discreet, white-glove transportation to and from Boeing Field. We coordinate with FBO operators and private terminals to ensure seamless pickups and drop-offs.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Whether you are arriving on a private charter or departing on a corporate jet, our professional chauffeurs are trained to handle high-profile clients with the utmost privacy and professionalism.
          </p>
          <a href="/book-now" class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all">
            Book Your Boeing Field Transfer
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Boeing Field Service Features</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">FBO Coordination</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We coordinate directly with your FBO for seamless arrivals</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Private Terminal Access</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Direct access to private jet terminals and ramps</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Executive Fleet</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cadillac Escalade ESV, Mercedes S-Class, luxury sedans</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Discreet and Professional</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Trained for high-profile and corporate client expectations</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Corporate Accounts</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Monthly billing and account management available</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Flight Tracking</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Real-time monitoring for charter and private flights</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Serve -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Who Uses Our Boeing Field Service</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Specialized transportation for every type of Boeing Field traveler</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✈️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Private Jet Travelers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Luxury transportation coordinated with your FBO. Arrive at the ramp in style with no commercial airport hassle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">💼</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Corporate Executives</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Seattle area companies use Boeing Field for corporate shuttles. We provide reliable executive transportation with account billing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🏢</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Boeing Employees</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Transportation for Boeing staff, contractors, and visitors to Boeing Field facilities and the Museum of Flight.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Boeing Field Info -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About Boeing Field (BFI)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Full Name:</strong> King County International Airport</li>
            <li><strong>IATA Code:</strong> BFI</li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> 3 miles south of downtown Seattle</li>
            <li><strong>Primary Use:</strong> Private, charter, cargo and Boeing test flights</li>
            <li><strong>Notable Tenants:</strong> Boeing, Museum of Flight, multiple FBOs</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> 7277 Perimeter Rd S, Seattle, WA 98108</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Nearby Destinations</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Downtown Seattle:</strong> 10-15 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>South Seattle:</strong> 5-10 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>Renton (Boeing):</strong> 15-20 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>Bellevue:</strong> 20-30 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>SeaTac Airport:</strong> 15-20 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>Tacoma:</strong> 35-45 minutes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Boeing Field Limo FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you service private jet terminals at Boeing Field?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We coordinate with all FBO operators at Boeing Field including Clay Lacy Aviation, Galvin Flying, and others to arrange direct ramp access or terminal pickups.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Boeing Field closer to downtown Seattle than SeaTac?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. Boeing Field is just 3 miles from downtown Seattle, making it significantly closer than SeaTac which is 14 miles away. For private flights, BFI is often the preferred choice for Seattle city access.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer corporate accounts for Boeing Field service?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We offer corporate accounts with monthly billing, priority booking, and dedicated account management for businesses that regularly use Boeing Field.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can you transport groups from Boeing Field?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We have SUVs and can coordinate multiple vehicles for larger groups arriving on charter flights. Contact us for group transportation quotes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Book Your Boeing Field Limo Service</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-200">
        Premium transportation for private jet and charter flight passengers at BFI
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK NOW
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          Call (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
